                    <p>闪迪至尊极速 Extreme SSD 今日开启京东秒杀，1TB 低至 396 元。</p><p>下单 1 件抽 1000 京豆（中奖率 99.99％），晒单抽 50E 卡（中奖率 99.99％），折合低至 336 元：</p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/2OVYlhm" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/264926/21/24480/28621/67bea09bF2d8c9f5f/052c3c116ba813d9.png" title="5150MB/s：闪迪至尊极速固态 1TB 秒杀 336 元近期新低" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">闪迪 至尊极速 SSD 1TB</span></span><span class="card-abstract">TLC 颗粒 PCIe 4.0</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price"> 实付 396 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p>闪迪至尊极速固态硬盘采用 PCIe 4.0 协议，顺序读取速度可达 5150MB/s，顺序写入速度 4850MB/s，随机读取速度 650K IOPS，随机写入速度 800K IOPS。</p><p><img height="599" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/10/189edef6-729d-4f52-9d78-0df1caf614d4.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="5150MB/s：闪迪至尊极速固态 1TB 秒杀 336 元近期新低" width="934" /><img height="1139" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/7/b740ab54-450a-42d9-89da-39fbbe0900c1.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="5150MB/s：闪迪至尊极速固态 1TB 秒杀 336 元近期新低" width="1172" /></p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/2OVYlhm" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/264926/21/24480/28621/67bea09bF2d8c9f5f/052c3c116ba813d9.png" title="5150MB/s：闪迪至尊极速固态 1TB 秒杀 336 元近期新低" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">闪迪 至尊极速 SSD 1TB</span></span><span class="card-abstract">TLC 颗粒 PCIe 4.0</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price"> 实付 396 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p class="ad-tips">广告声明：文内含有的对外跳转链接（包括不限于超链接、二维码、口令等形式），用于传递更多信息，节省甄选时